    @Entity
public class StringPath
extends AbstractPath<String>
    AbstractPath implementation using Strings for path elements. Note! This implementation is immutable, implying that the append method returns a new instance, rather than modifying this one.
    Author:
    Lennart Jörelid, jGuru Europe AB
